tv.amwa.maj.constant

Interface RP224FirstHalf

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    RP224

    public interface RP224FirstHalf

    First half of constants from SMPTE RP224, the SMPTE Labels Registry.

    Splitting into two is required due to Java initialiser limits.

    See Also:
    RP224
